<tr>
<td class="mainleft">&nbsp;</td>
<td class="main"><br>






<p>Lets start with the basics. Even many veterans could learn a
lesson from the following.</p>

<p class="title">Gameplay Types and Objectives</p>

<p>These are your objectives for each type of game listed in order
of priority. It should be noted that wiping out the entire enemy
team is never a primary objective. You will earn more money by
completing the primary objectives.</p>

<p class="title">Bomb Planting/Defusal (de maps)</p>

<p>Counter-Terrorists</p>

<p>1. Prevent placement of the bomb - Once you have secured the
bomb sites or the bomb itself you should not be tempted to move, if
the bomb cannot be armed by the terrorists then they cannot win.
Often attempts to hunt down the remaining terrorists ends in tears
as your lured into an ambush or they retake the bomb and manage to
plant it.</p>

<p>2. Defuse the bomb - If you fail to achieve the first goal your
second is to defuse the bomb. For this reason always buy a defuse
kit if you have the money. Be aware that terrorists will often
ambush you after you start to defuse the bomb, make sure the area
is secure if you have the time.</p>

<p>Terrorists</p>

<p>1. Place and defend the bomb - As a terrorist your only
objective is to reach a bomb site, place the bomb and then to
defend it. You will earn the wrath of you team if as the bomb
carrier you fail to plant the bomb after they have secured the bomb
site for you.</p>

<p class="title">Hostage Taking/Rescue (cs maps)</p>

<p>Counter-Terrorists</p>

<p>Terrorists</p>

<p class="title">VIP Assasination/Protection (as maps)</p>

<p>Counter-Terrorists</p>

<p>Terrorists</p>

